    &lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: Celebrating the small victories of 2025. Hegseth demotes retired Navy Captain Mark Kelly as Trump regime cuts funding for poor families in Democratic states. ICE murders 2 U.S. citizens in 8 days. Is our undeclared war with Venezuela legal?&lt;/p&gt;
