&lt;section class=&quot;block the-bad&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Hegseth attacks veteran Mark Kelly&#39;s retirement pay &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theatlantic.com/newsletters/2026/01/hegseth-mark-kelly-demotion-vengeance/685512/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;

    &lt;a href=&quot;/images/nuCzDPftNv-500.webp&quot; class=&quot;lightbox-link&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;cursor:zoom-in&quot;&gt;
      &lt;img class=&quot;img-lightbox&quot; alt=&quot;Senator Mark Kelly, 2021&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/nuCzDPftNv-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;625&quot; srcset=&quot;/images/nuCzDPftNv-200.webp 200w, /images/nuCzDPftNv-500.webp 500w&quot; sizes=&quot;200px&quot;&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;
            &lt;blockquote&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;Our laws are clear: You can refuse illegal orders.&lt;/p&gt;
