				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.propublica.org/article/sean-duffy-trump-transportation-secretary-congress-funding&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(ProPublica) Trump&#39;s Transportation Secretary Sean Duffy once defended Congress&#39; power of the purse. Now he defies it&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
