    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        U.S. military seizes merchant oil tanker &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/12/11/g-s1-101668/seized-oil-tanker-off-the-coast-venezuela&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
