				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/pete-hegseth-drug-boats-navy-admiral-b2877882.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(The Independent) The departure of Admiral Alvin Holsey, head of U.S. Southern Command, has stunned lawmakers and military experts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr style=&quot;clear:both&quot;/&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Costco sues Trump regime, demands refund for tariffs &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aljazeera.com/economy/2025/12/2/costco-sues-trump-administration-for-us-tariff-refund&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;
            &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Costco building in North Plainfield, New Jersey&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/AKqbrfks5a-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;149&quot;&gt;
