            &lt;p&gt;But Greene ultimately failed Trump&#39;s loyalty test when she refused to toe the party line on the genocide in Gaza and the release of the Epstein files. True to his nature, Donny 2-Dolls went from praising Greene to chastising her to openly threatening her. He called her a traitor and a ranting lunatic for saying that he should release the Epstein files, even though a week later he ordered all Republicans to vote to release the files.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;Greene seemed surprised that Donny 2-Dolls would turn on her, despite the fact that he has never treated his supporters any better than his enemies. Let this be a little life lesson to Greene: If you&#39;re going to cheer for a bully, don&#39;t be surprised if he turns around and starts to bully you.&lt;/p&gt;            
