		&lt;/ol&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;While these elections are encouraging, we do want to point out that this was an off-year election with only a few states or cities that had significant candidates or policies on the ballot at all. Hopefully, these results are a sign that people are fed up with the Trump regime&#39;s assault on American democracy. If this momentum keeps up, it&#39;s entirely possible that the 2026 mid-term elections will significantly change the balance of power in our government.&lt;/p&gt;
