        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;This week, the government shutdown officially became the longest in US history by surpassing the previous record, which was set during Donny 2-Dolls&#39; first term.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Democrats continue to demand Republicans negotiate with them&amp;mdash;the historically successful way to end government shutdowns. Republicans, however, have refused to negotiate on any budget issues, and House Speaker Johnson has refused to even conduct the business of the House that he is being paid to conduct during the shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;
