        Trump regime will make it harder to qualify for disability benefits &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.propublica.org/article/social-security-disability-eligibility-trump-red-states&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
