        Trump deploys largest warship in US arsenal to Latin America &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aljazeera.com/video/newsfeed/2025/10/25/maduro-accuses-trump-of-fabricating-war-as-us-deploys-largest-warship&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
