                    &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/government-shutdown-expected-drag-least-week-rcna235407&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(NBC) Government shutdown to drag into at least next week, with House out until Oct. 14&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
