    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Arrest of Newark Mayor Ras Baraka at an ICE facility in May was planned, staged, and executed on orders from the deputy attorney general of the United States. The arrest was carried out &lt;i&gt;despite&lt;/i&gt; the fact that there was no reasonable justification...the mayor had already left the facility by the time the decision was made to arrest him.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;The ICE-stapo agents are briefed by an officer and given direct orders&amp;mdash;as they are preparing to make an arrest&amp;mdash;to turn &lt;b&gt;off&lt;/b&gt; their body cams. I can&#39;t think of any more clear sign that an agent is about to do something immoral or illegal than being told &lt;i&gt;in advance&lt;/i&gt; to turn off their body cam.&lt;/p&gt;
